{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"c37a6ac7-d200-470c-ac19-34eb29ad310c","content":"Here are the issues I found in the `.template.config/template.json`:\n\n**Error:**\n- **Line 9** — `\"datatype\": \"invalid-type\"` is not a valid datatype. Valid values for a .NET template parameter are: `bool`, `choice`, `float`, `int`, `hex`, `text`, or `string`.\n\n**Warnings (recommended but optional):**\n- **Missing `identity`** — It's best practice to include an `\"identity\"` field to uniquely identify the template.\n- **Missing `$schema`** — Adding `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"` enables editor validation and autocomplete.\n\nThe invalid `datatype` on `myParam` is the critical issue — the template engine will reject or ignore this parameter at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"a4082e04-c466-437f-9518-82b79ecd52be","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"Let me analyze this template.json file. This is a .NET template configuration file (used by `dotnet new`). Let me check for issues:\n\n1. **`$schema`** - Missing. It's recommended to include `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"` for validation.\n\n2. **`author`** - Present, value \"Test\". ✓\n\n3. **`classifications`** - Present, array of strings. ✓\n\n4. **`name`** - Present. ✓\n\n5. **`identity`** - Missing. While not strictly required, it's recommended for uniqueness.\n\n\n6. **`shortName`** - Present, value \"build\". ✓\n\n7. **`symbols.myParam.datatype`** - Value is `\"invalid-type\"`. The valid datatype values for a .NET template parameter are: `bool`, `choice`, `float`, `int`, `hex`, `text`, `string`. `\"invalid-type\"` is not a valid datatype.\n\n8. **`sourceName`** - Missing, but optional.\n\n9. **`tags`** - Missing, but optional.\n\nThe critical issue here is that `symbols.myParam.datatype` uses an invalid type that won't be recognized by the template engine. I should also check if there are other files in the working directory to understand the broader context and identify any other configuration problems.","outputTokens":576,"requestId":"A7C2:155537:168725D:1913185:6A051E56"},"id":"31f439e5-70b8-40f5-aec9-26c9fba597ed","timestamp":"2026-05-14T00:59:14.703Z","parentId":"55cd3a2f-28ef-4842-9c69-650a11b0b4db"}
